Package com.jackmeng.cosmos.events

Class FVRightClick

java.lang.Object
java.awt.event.MouseAdapter
com.jackmeng.cosmos.events.FVRightClick
All Implemented Interfaces:
MouseListener, MouseMotionListener, MouseWheelListener, EventListener
public class FVRightClick extends MouseAdapter
This class handles the right click event for any JTree instance. This right click menu currently allows the user to hide a node from view.
Since:
3.0
Author:
Jack Meng
See Also:
JTree, DefaultMutableTreeNode
